query:
SELECT 
  mes, 
  ano, 
  CAST(SUM(totalServicos) AS SIGNED) as totalServicos,
  CAST(SUM(objetivoMensal) AS SIGNED) as objetivoMensal,
  COUNT(DISTINCT lojaId) as totalLojas
FROM resultados_mensais
GROUP BY mes, ano
ORDER BY ano DESC, mes DESC
LIMIT 8
